Available Tools: create_subscription | cancel_subscription | pause_subscription | update_plan | get_subscription
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "customer_id": "string", "plan_id": "string", "trial_days": number }
Response Schema: { "subscription_id": "string", "status": "active|canceled|paused|trialing", "plan": "string", "current_period_end": "string" }
---
Question: Initiate a basic plan subscription for client cli_4455 with a 10-day trial window.
Call: { "func_call": "create_subscription", "customer_id": "cli_4455", "plan_id": "basic", "trial_days": 10 }
Response: { "subscription_id": "sub_1100m", "status": "trialing", "plan": "basic", "current_period_end": "2023-11-18T00:00:00Z" }

Question: End the premium service for user usr_7788 associated with subscription sub_3322n.
Call: { "func_call": "cancel_subscription", "customer_id": "usr_7788", "plan_id": "premium", "trial_days": 0 }
